## Purpose
##    Template and macros for a page with embedded google map
##
## Revision Dates
##    24-Feb-2010 (CT) Creation (ported from Django template)
##     4-Dec-2012 (CT) Remove `http:` (--> protocol-relative)
##     3-Dec-2015 (CT) Add `max-height`, `max-width`;
